programme.title: Cheers: Paint Your Office
programme.desc: Norm blir bedre kjent med Rebecca da han maler kontoret hennes i et forsøk på å nedbetale barregningen.

programme.title: Cheers: The Last Angry Mailman
programme.desc: En butikkjede vil gjerne kjøpe Cliffs familiehjem og bygge det om til et supermarked, men Cliff motsetter seg planene. Gjengen får vite at Rebeccas kallenavn på skolen var "Backseat Becky".

programme.title: Cheers: Bidding on the Boys
programme.desc: Sam og Woody byr seg frem for salg på en auksjon til inntekt for et veldedig formål, men de er ikke særlig begeistret over sine nye "eiere".

programme.title: Cheers: Puddinhead Boyd
programme.desc: Woody innleder et forhold til en gammel dame, som han møtte mens han var utkledd som Mark Twain.

programme.title: Cheers: A Kiss Is Still a Kiss
programme.desc: Rebecca mener at sjefen hennes har fått feil inntrykk av henne, og for å rette på det ber hun Sam om å bli med henne på et jobbarrangement.
programme.sub-title: A Kiss Is Still a Kiss

programme.title: Cheers: My Fair Clavin
programme.desc: Cliff hjelper kjæresten sin med å forbedre utseende sitt, men angrer når hun får oppmerksomhet fra alle kanter, også fra Sam.

programme.title: Cheers: Christmas Cheers
programme.desc: Julaften blir en trist affære i baren etter at Rebecca ber alle om å jobbe sent.

programme.title: Cheers: Woody for Hire Meets Norman of the Apes
programme.desc: Woody prøver å overbevise vennene sine om at han har fått en rolle i en TV-serie.
programme.sub-title: Woody for Hire Meets Norman of the Apes

programme.title: Cheers: And God Created Woodman
programme.desc: Woody tar på seg skylden da Rebecca knuser en vase på en firmafest, og han ender opp som kompis med sjefen.

programme.title: Cheers: Tale of Two Cuties
programme.desc: Til Rebeccas store forargelse ansetter Mr. Drake en pen, ung kvinne som bartender på Cheers.

programme.title: Cheers: Yacht of Fools
programme.desc: Evan Drake inviterer Rebecca og Sam til å tilbringe en helg om bord i båten hans.

programme.title: Cheers: To All the Girls I've Loved Before
programme.desc: Frasiers utdrikningslag utvikler seg til en dyster feiring.
programme.sub-title: To All the Girls I've Loved Before

programme.title: Cheers: Let Sleeping Drakes Lie
programme.desc: Rebecca blir tatt på fersk gjerning på Evan Drakes soverom.

programme.title: Cheers: Airport V
programme.desc: Carla får hjelp av Frasier til å overvinne flyskrekken. Rebecca venter i spenning på et besøk fra en restaurantkritiker.

programme.title: Cheers: The Sam in the Gray Flannel Suit
programme.desc: Rebecca blir sjalu når Sam blir forfremmet, helt til hun får vite årsaken til forfremmelsen.

programme.title: Cheers: Our Hourly Bread
programme.desc: Woody foreslår for Rebecca at de lodder ut en ferie i Karibien for å få baren ut av det økonomiske uføret.

programme.title: Cheers: Slumber Party Massacred
programme.desc: Etter at Carla får vite at hun snart skal bli bestemor, inviterer Lilith og Rebecca henne på overnattingsfest for å muntre henne opp.

programme.title: Spin City: In the Heat of the Day
programme.desc: Da politiet uretfærdigt arresterer Carter, lærer Mike og personalet, at racisme er mere end blot et sort-hvidt problem.
programme.sub-title: In the Heat of the Day

programme.title: Spin City: Radio Daze
programme.desc: Der kommer gnister i luften, da en sportsradiovært udfordrer borgmesteren til en popularitetskonkurrence.

programme.title: Spin City: The 30 Year Itch
programme.desc: Mens hans kolleger kæmper for at finde en unik fødselsdagsgave til Mike i anledning af hans 30 års fødselsdag, fejrer han dagen med sin første flamme.

programme.title: Spin City: My Life Is a Soap Opera
programme.desc: Mikes liv udspiller sig bogstaveligt talt for øjnene af ham, da han begynder at date en sæbeopera-forfatter.
programme.sub-title: My Life Is a Soap Opera

programme.title: Spin City: The Family - part 1
programme.desc: Nikki dater en bugtaler, der tilsyneladende ikke fungerer uden sin dukke. Mikes mor indleder til gengæld et forhold til borgmesteren…

programme.title: Spin City: The Family - part 2
programme.desc: Til Mikes forfærdelse er hans mor den eneste person, der kan hjælpe borgmesteren ud af falske anklager, om at han ofte har besøgt en sexarbejder.

programme.title: Spin City: They Shoot Horses, Don't They?
programme.desc: Mens borgmesterens datter er hjemme på ferie fra college, arrangerer hun en dristig protest for dyrerettigheder, der kommer på forsiderne.

programme.title: Spin City: Miracle Near 34th Street
programme.desc: Det er juletid, men Mike får hænderne fulde, da nogle julemænd protesterer mod at blive fyret og borgmesteren kvajer sig.

programme.title: Spin City: The Paul Lassiter Story
programme.desc: Paul er ivrig efter omtale i borgmesterens kommende bog, og Mike står over for en medicinsk krise, der får ham til at genoverveje sine prioriteter.

programme.title: Spin City: Gentlemen's Agreement
programme.desc: Borgmesterens medlemskab i en eksklusiv herreklub sætter gang i en storm hos pressen.

programme.title: Spin City: Deaf Man Walking
programme.desc: Staceys bedstemor forbander Mike, efter at han opfordrer Stacey til at flytte ud af familiens hjem.

programme.title: Spin City: The Marrying Men
programme.desc: En af Mikes ekskærester vender tilbage i hans liv og antager fejlagtigt, at en forlovelsesring, som han holder for Paul, er beregnet til hende.

programme.title: Spin City: One Wedding and a Funeral
programme.desc: Mikes forlovelse skaber kaos i Paus kærlighedsliv og inspirerer fantasier fra Mikes kvindelige medarbejdere.

programme.title: Spin City: A River Runs Through Me
programme.desc: Mike har svært ved at bestå en narkotikatest på arbejdspladsen, efter at han utilsigtet har indtaget et hallucinogen under en oprindelig-amerikansk ceremoni.

programme.title: Spin City: The Pope of Gracie Mansion
programme.desc: Et besøg fra paven giver Mike et slag af gudfrygtighed.

programme.title: Spin City: The Lady or the Tiger
programme.desc: Mikes forhold til en kvindelig tryllekunstner går lige så hurtigt galt som Stuart Bondek og Carters bar for homoseksuelle går godt.

programme.title: Spin City: Single White Male
programme.desc: Carter giver modvilligt Stuart lov til at flytte ind hos ham, mens personalet prøver at fange en rotte, der lurer på kontoret.

programme.title: Spin City: The Paul-Bearer
programme.desc: Paul og Claudias bryllup kommer i problemer, fordi Mike reserverer kirken til den forkerte dag.

programme.title: Spin City: There's Something About Heidi
programme.desc: Nikki bliver jaloux på Mikes spirende flirt med supermodellen Heidi Klum.

programme.title: Spin City: The Deer Hunter
programme.desc: Mike håber på at få fat i en rig politisk donator, men det ser ud til, at han bliver nødt til at skyde en hjort for at det skal lykkes.

programme.title: Spin City: It Happened One Night
programme.desc: Mike beslutter sig for at adoptere en forladt baby, og James besøger en psykiater på borgmesterens vegne.

programme.title: Spin City: Quest For Fire
programme.desc: Mens borgmesteren forbereder sig på at bære den olympiske fakkel, opfinder Nikki en kæreste, og Paul prøver at passe ind i sit nye kvarter.

programme.title: Spin City: The Kidney's All Right
programme.desc: En fejlinformation fra borgmesteren får Mike til at blive uvillig organdonor.

programme.title: Spin City: Local Hero
programme.desc: Et desillusioneret byrådsmedlem beslutter at droppe sit job og blive en rigtig superhelt ved navn Kaptajn New York.

programme.title: Spin City: Monkey Business
programme.desc: Et yderst intelligent chimpanse får Mike til at ligne en idiot, mens Stuart og Carter fejrer deres første jul som samboer.

programme.title: Spin City: Taxi Driver
programme.desc: En taxastrejke kan ske at sætte bremserne i Mikes forsøg på at ødelægge Nikkis lidenskabelige romance.

programme.title: Spin City: Dick Clark's Rockin Make-Up Party
programme.desc: Der er kærlighed i luften for Mike, borgmesteren og James, men retssager i luften for Stuart.

programme.title: Spin City: Back to the Future IV: Judgement Day
programme.desc: Mikes politiske mentor hævder at være Messias.
programme.sub-title: Back to the Future IV: Judgement Day

programme.title: Spin City: Politically Incorrect
programme.desc: Borgmesteren afslører en sexet hemmelighed under sin gæsteoptræden på Politically Incorrect, og Carter afslører sin kærestes seksuelle orientering.

programme.title: Spin City: The Last Temptation of Mike
programme.desc: Paul spørger Mike om at gøre sin kone gravid.

programme.title: MTV Cribs: Kristin Cavallari / Leslie Allen Jordan / Ray J
programme.desc: MTV-kongeligheten Kristin Cavallari viser oss sitt sjarmerende hjemsted i Nashville. Sydstats-kjendistanten Leslie Allen Jordan viser ungkarsbula si i Los Angeles. Så tar MTV en vill tur med R&B-sangeren Ray J i hans ray-koniske herresete i Miami.
programme.sub-title: Kristin Cavallari / Leslie Allen Jordan / Ray J

programme.title: MTV Cribs: Whitney Cummings / Dennis Rodman

programme.title: MTV Cribs: Iman Shumpert / Heidi and Spencer Pratt / Cesar Millan
programme.desc: Vi tar en tur i basketspiller og familiemann Iman Shumperts krypinn i Los Angeles. Deretter sonderer vi terrenget hos realitylegendene Heidi og Spencer Pratt. Speidi. Turen slutter hos Cesar Millans dyrerike.
programme.sub-title: Iman Shumpert / Heidi and Spencer Pratt / Cesar Millan

programme.desc: On the morning of January 9th 2014, Josiane Bézard, 53 years old, drives her son to the Manosque's train station, and then vanishes.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Stabed In Her Bed: The Maureen Jaquier Case
programme.desc: On February 27, 2015, in Toulouse, the parents of 19-year-old Maureen Jacquier discover their daughter stabbed several times in her bed.
programme.sub-title: Stabed In Her Bed: The Maureen Jaquier Case

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: One Step Ahead Part 1
programme.desc: It's Zigfried vs. Leon for the right to challenge Yugi in the KC Grand Championship Finals... but Kaiba stops the duel!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: One Step Ahead Part 2
programme.desc: It's a battle between Zigfried and Kaiba. Zigfried quickly gains the advantage by destroying Kaiba's monsters before he can even draw them!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Sinister Secrets Part 1
programme.desc: It's Yugi vs. Leon for the title of King of Games at the KC Grand Championship! Something sinister lurks in the shadows, for this duel is more than just getting the crown. Zigfried's greatest revenge will commence as his real plan is unleashed.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Sinister Secrets Part 2
programme.desc: Leon is Zigfried's younger brother, and he'll avenge his family's loss. Leon's fairy tales are giving Yugi nightmares but the worst is yet to come as Leon has Zigfried's mysterious and special card.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Sinister Secrets Part 3
programme.desc: Golden Castle of Stromberg is infecting the world's Duel Disks with a virus that will destroy KaibaCorp. If Yugi doesn't destroy the card, the virus program can't be stopped.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Getting Played
programme.desc: The gang goes on an exotic trip to India, but when their plane crashes in a deserted forest, their vacation turns into a dangerous game of survival.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Divide and Conquer
programme.desc: Realizing that they've become part of a real-life version of the Capsule Monsters board game, the gang struggles to find a way out.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: The Hands of Justice Part II
programme.desc: Jaden is shown a disturbing vision of our planet's fate should he lose to the Light of Destruction!
programme.sub-title: The Hands of Justice Part II

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Future Changes
programme.desc: The future looks bleak as the Light of Destruction continues to overwhelm Jaden while a brainwashing satellite pointing towards Earth is activated!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Third Times the Charm
programme.desc: Jaden reflects on last year's adventures as he prepares for the third year at Duel Academy!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: A Jewel of a Duel, Part 1
programme.desc: Jaden meets North Academy's top student Jesse Anderson, a duelist who can speak to monster spirits - just like Jaden can!
programme.sub-title: A Jewel of a Duel, Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: A Jewel of a Duel, Part 2
programme.desc: Jaden's duel against Jesse continues as we learn the origins of Jesse's mysterious Crystal Beast cards.
programme.sub-title: A Jewel of a Duel, Part 2

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Hanging with Axel, Part 1
programme.desc: Syrus is kidnapped by Duel Academy's new bad boy Axel Brodie, and only Jaden can save him… by dueling Axel!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Hanging with Axel, Part 2
programme.desc: Jaden's duel against Axel continues as Syrus's life hangs by a thread… literally!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Primal Instinct
programme.desc: Strange electromagnetic waves ignite Hassleberry's animal instincts as he battles Jim Cook and his pet crocodile Shirley!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Head in the Clouds, Part 1
programme.desc: Furious that he's no longer the richest kid in school, Chazz challenges billionaire Adrian Gecko to a duel in the sky!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Head in the Clouds, Part 2
programme.desc: With his powerful deck of cloud monsters, Adrian Gecko takes Chazz by storm!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Win Mr. Stein's Duel, Part 1
programme.desc: While searching for Viper, Jaden encounters a former teacher who has one final test for him!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Win Mr. Stein's Duel, Part 2
programme.desc: Jaden and Professor Stein's duel continues as Jaden tries to stay awake to learn one last lesson.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Trapper Keeper, Part 1
programme.desc: Jesse and Jaden are on the hunt for Viper… until Jesse's Crystal Beasts become the hunted!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Trapper Keeper, Part 2
programme.desc: Jesse's duel against Trapper continues as Jesse fights to free his Crystal Beasts from Trapper's traps!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: A Snake in the Grass, Part 1
programme.desc: Professor Viper raises the stakes by forcing Jaden to duel on a tower where the only way down is a 20-story drop!
programme.sub-title: A Snake in the Grass, Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: A Snake in the Grass, Part 2
programme.desc: Jaden continues his duel with Viper, but in a swamp full of serpents and snakes, will he be able to find victory?
programme.sub-title: A Snake in the Grass, Part 2

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: A Snake in the Grass, Part 3
programme.desc: It's now or never as Jaden tries to defeat Viper and his snakes before they swallow up Jaden's life points for good.
programme.sub-title: A Snake in the Grass, Part 3

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Inter-Dimension Detention
programme.desc: Jaden and his friends find themselves in a different dimension where duel monsters are real, the ocean is a sea of sand and... Wait, class is still in session?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Sub-Desert Duel
programme.desc: After one of their classmates becomes ill, the gang ventures off to find a deserted submarine in the desert. Can they find what they're looking for, or is someone out to sink their plans before they get there?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Night of the Living Duelist
programme.desc: As an army of Duel Ghouls slowly takes over Duel Academy, can Jaden and his friends figure out a way to duel these ghouls, or will they all get schooled in the process?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: School Ghoul Duels
programme.desc: It's an all-out battle with the Duel Ghouls as Jaden tries to get Blair the medicine she needs. Will she get the first aid in time, or have the Duel Ghouls prescribed a different kind of treatment for her?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Triple Play, Part 1
programme.desc: When three rogue students go looking for food, they end up biting off more than they can chew. And when Jaden gets challenged, it soon becomes a battle with triple the action, triple the duels, and triple the danger!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Triple Play, Part 2
programme.desc: With Jesse, Jim, and Axel facing off against three masked duelists, there's no telling what might happen. It's an all-out battle where the winners get their just desserts and the losers just get hungry!

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 105
programme.desc: Sabine fant et tilbud på nettet, men måtte betale dyrt for å spare 50 prosent.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 608
programme.desc: I 2011 velger Sabina å ta en brystforstørrelsesoperasjon. Men allerede et par dager etter operasjonen oppdager hun at brystene hennes henger.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 202
programme.desc: I dagens episode møter vi bl.a. Pernille, som føler seg fanget i sitt eget hjem, og Linda, som er så hemmet av et arr på magen at hun møter opp tidlig på jobb for å unngå å skifte med andre.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 902
programme.desc: Etter en brystoperasjon har Samantha tunge, smertefulle bryster og et skrantende forhold.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 609
programme.desc: For 21 år siden havnet Allan i en voldsom sykkelulykke. Allan er merket for livet, og til tross for flere operasjoner sitter han igjen med arr i ansiktet.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 306
programme.desc: Vi møter Jeanette, som føler seg som en forsøkskanin etter en rekke mislykkede operasjoner. Maria måtte fjerne implantatene sine, og er nå uten bryster. Shahin har smerter etter en ansiktsløftning.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 311
programme.desc: I denne episoden møter vi bl.a. Maria, som etter 11 operasjoner har fått det hun kaller verdens styggeste bryster. Rose fikk en bredere nese etter at hun opererte den.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 405
programme.desc: I denne episoden møter vi Jette, som har valgt ikke å amme sine tre barn på grunn av silikonbrystene sine, og Charlotte som fremdeles har kjøttsår på innsiden av låret etter fettsuging.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 103
programme.desc: Ivana endte ikke bare opp med å bruke en million kroner i USA, men hun ble også offer for en fatal beslutning, tatt av legene mens hun lå i narkose

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 604
programme.desc: Gjennom hele livet har 61 år gamle Lis ønsket å forandre sine små bryster. Derfor valgte hun å ta en brystforstørrelsesoperasjon, men kort tid etter opplevde hun at det påvirket sexlivet hennes.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 903
programme.desc: Nanna har hatt flere brystoperasjoner og korrigeringer, men sitter nå igjen med deformerte, harde bryster. På grunn av operasjonene vil hun ikke at noen skal se henne naken.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 406
programme.desc: I denne episoden møter vi Anita som våkner opp med større bryster enn hun hadde avtalt med kirurgen og nå føler seg som en mini-versjon av Linse Kessler.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 603
programme.desc: For tre år siden valgte Sarah å ta en brystforstørrelsesoperasjon i Polen, men etter operasjonen syntes hun brystene hennes så ut som to kaffeposer med implantater.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 613
programme.desc: Når sønnen endelig blir frisk, føler Charlott seg ikke lenger som seg selv, og hun velger derfor å ta en brystforstørrelsesoperasjon. Men resultatet ble en stor skuffelse.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 407
programme.desc: Vi møter Maria, som etter en brystoperasjon fikk store abscesser og hull helt inn til implantatet.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Cardiff Carnage!
programme.desc: Anna sier til gjengen at de skal dra til Cardiff. Beau er forventningsfull fordi alle kommer til å treffe broren hans, Harvey, som bor der. Men det gjør Bethan nervøs. Familien har det fint i Wales og Tahlia kliner med Harvey.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Dizzy Heights!
programme.desc: Geordierne har hjemmefest! Det er masse gøy og klining på gang. Beau foretrekker Bethan fremfor Abbie. Dette fører til en krangel mellom Chloe og Nathan - igjen! Scott syns lagånden bør styrkes så de rappellerer.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Fight Night!
programme.desc: Nathan arrangerer en overraskelsesfest for sin singelbestevenn, Tahila. Aaron ringer huset og inviterer familien som støtte på hans første MMA-kamp i Newcastle. Alle stiller opp for Aaron, og familien drar i svært godt humør.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Meet The Newbies
programme.desc: Den nye Geordie Shore-serien begynner snart, men først har Scotty samlet det meste av gjengen for å prate om showet. Samt å treffe de siste fire tilskuddene, håndplukket av ham som folk som alle karakterene vil feste med.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Shake Ups & Break Ups!
programme.desc: Alt er ikke bra i Toon! Chloe og Sam har slått opp og gjengen er urolige for hvordan det kommer til å påvirke familien. James og Abbie er tilbake i huset, men første kveld slutter i katastrofe når Beau sier til Bethan at det er slutt.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Give It Another Go!
programme.desc: Sam forstår at han må sette seg og snakke igjennom tingene med Chloe, og forlater huset for en oppriktig og ærlig prat. Til slutt avgjør de å gi tingene en ny sjanse, men nyheten faller ikke bra ut hos resten av huset.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Tensions Keep Rising!
programme.desc: Chloe konfronterer jentene om at de ikke støtter henne i å gjenoppta forholdet med Sam. Sam gir Chloe en overraskelse, men oppførselen under guttekvelden fører til at de slår opp igjen! Abbie forteller James at hun så Chloe gå med en fyr på Ibiza.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Party in Portugal!
programme.desc: Sam fatter en stor avgjørelse når gjengen får høre at de skal i vei til Portugal. Tross dette lever familien som best de kan og fester på Algarve. Men spenningen mellom Bethan, Beau og Abbie truer med å koke over og ødelegge moroa.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Agg on the Algarve!
programme.desc: Bethan og Abbies krangel påvirker huset og alt tar av da Nat kaller Bethan og Beaus forhold 'forgiftet'. Men på ekte Geordie-stil legger familien det bak seg, blir sittene fast i sangria og river opp strippen.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Fun at the Fair!
programme.desc: Gjengen er tilbake fra Portugal, men Sam har forlatt huset, noe som får Chloe til å tro at det er slutt for alltid. Familien tar helt av i Newcastles største fornøyelsespark og Beau spør endelig Bethan om hun vil bli kjæresten hans offisielt.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Geordies Do the Great Outdoors!
programme.desc: Chloe besøker Sam og de gjør fremskritt i forholdet, mens de andre vil gå ut kledd som motsatt kjønn. Gjengen drar på camping og blir angrepet av mygg. James bestemmer seg for å fortelle Sam om Chloes kyss på Ibiza.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Breaking Point
programme.desc: James forteller Sam om Chloes kyss på Ibiza, og helvete er løs når Sam konfronterer henne. Chloe tror ikke at Abbie avslørte hemmeligheten, for det var bare et kyss. Men Sam ser det ikke slik og forlater huset for godt.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Beau's Birthday!
programme.desc: Chloe og Sam er ute av huset og gjengen konsentrerer seg om å more seg. Beau får en husfest med jungeltema - den er vill! James og Beau overrasker Nathan ved å invitere nettdaten hans, Tommy fra Amsterdam, over til Newcastle.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Serious Send Off!
programme.desc: Det er den siste hele dagen i huset, og gjengen forbereder en 'Big One'! Nathan lar Bethan gi ham voksning av baken. Nat lager et farvelmåltif til familien og Chloe blir med alle for siste kveld på Toon - det blir stilig!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Get This Party Started!
programme.desc: Geordierne er spente på å komme tilbake til huset og de føeste er single. De ønsker to nykommere, Amelia og Ant velkomne, og viser dem hvordan de fester. Alt er kos og moro helt til Nathan og Beau kommer nære hverandre. Alt for nære for Bethan.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Jewish Barbie
programme.desc: Angelina og Vinny prøver å sameksistere, Deena er kanskje ikke den eneste som er kjøttbollegravid, og det blir déjà vu når Ronnie hopper i boblebadet med Angelinas venn.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Pork Roll eller Taylor Ham?
programme.desc: Gjengen savner den klumsete Deena, så de bestemmer seg for å kidnappe henne. Og hva skjer når Ronnie inviterer 'Jewish Barbie' til å overnatte på rommet hans?

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Wallopin' in Manalapan
programme.desc: Det er tid for hevn når romkameratene er ute etter idioten som plager dem i baren.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Ronnie Magro's Series of Unfortunate Events
programme.desc: I sesongfinalen kjemper Deena og romkameratene mot kreft. Spiralgjengen diskuterer meningen med livet. Og en mystisk telefonsamtale fra Jen gjør Ronnies liv enda mer dramatisk.
programme.sub-title: Ronnie Magro's Series of Unfortunate Events

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The United States vs. The Situation Part 1
programme.desc: Denne gangen samles de for å støtte sin bror, Mike. Dette er uken da dommen for skatteunndragelsen faller. Jwowws ekteskap krakelerer, men hun snakker heller om Angelinas forhold enn sitt eget.
programme.sub-title: The United States vs. The Situation Part 1

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The United States vs. The Situation Part 2
programme.desc: Hva er et passende rettssalsantrekk? Hvorfor har Ronnie en blåveis? Og hvor lang straff får Mike for skatteunndragelse?
programme.sub-title: The United States vs. The Situation Part 2

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Secaucus!
programme.desc: Følelsene slår enhver rekord da alle prøver å samle seg etter de sjokkerende detaljene rundt Mikes straffeutmåling.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The Dude Ranch
programme.desc: Med Mikes straffeutmåling bak seg, drar romkameratene nordover til en kompis ranch for en helgeutflukt. Guido-familien forsøker å fiske, Snooki drikker som en fisk og Ronnie forteller spøkelseshistorier foran leirbålet.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Ranchelor Party
programme.desc: Jentene inviterer Lauren-familien til kompisens ranch for Mikes overraskelse utdrikningslag. Imidlertid har Pauly og Vinny selv utvidet invitasjonen til en gjeng med strippere. Det oppstår en situasjon!

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Not So Shore
programme.desc: Det anonyme brevet skaper spenning mellom jentene, og det ender i slåsskamp. Etter enda en natt med Vinny avslører Snooki en ikke så lite kjent 'hemmelighet'.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Sleeping with the Enemy
programme.desc: Gjengen må takle konsekvensene av jentenes krangel. Angelina dater Jose fra klubben, og Jenni og Snooki kler seg i hjemmelagde beskyttelsesdrakter for å rydde opp før Snookis date.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: All in the Family
programme.desc: Mike truer med å fortelle Jose om Angelina og Vinny. Vinnys familie kommer på besøk. Og Vinny og Pauly finner drømmejentene, men en vil få knust hjertet sitt.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Dirty Pad
programme.desc: Angelina er i trøbbel når gjengen får vite at hun lå med Jose etter en natt med Vin. Men den siste dråpen kommer når Mike oppdager flere ubehageligheter på badet.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Gone, Baby, Gone
programme.desc: Mike gjenforens med sin kanadiske skjønnhet, til stor underholdning for hele huset. Angelina forteller gjengen hva hun syns om dem, noe som gjør Snooki rasende og får begeret til å flyte over.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Girls Like That
programme.desc: Vinny velger mellom to grupper jenter. Siden Angelina er borte vil Snooki at hun og Jenni skal skvære opp med Sam. Gleden blir kortvarig for Snooki, når Mike blir stadig mer fiendtlig.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Deja Vu All Over Again
programme.desc: Alle er frustrerte over Mike - han får gjengen sparket ut av en klubben, får bilen tauet vekk, brenner nesten ned huset og svikter Pauly. To ganger.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Dansekonkurransen
programme.desc: En ukoordinert Chase blir partneren til Zoey i en dansekonkurranse for de den gamle partneren hennes brakk beinet. Lola lurer noen til å tro at hun er fra England.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Frøken PCA
programme.desc: Lola og Zoey blir med i en skjønnhetskonkurranse som skaper en stor konflikt. Michael prøver å få Quinn til å synes at han er morsom.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Logan blir fattig
programme.desc: Rike Logan må forandre livstilen når faren slutter å sende ham penger. Michael sier at han kan komme seg ut av hva som helst, så Mark og Quinn binder ham fast for å se hva han får til.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Ha det Zoey - del 1
programme.desc: Zoey må ta en avgjørelse på om hun skal bli på PCA eller flytte til London med foreldrene. Hun ber vennene sine om råd, men unngår Chase så lenge hun kan.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Ha det Zoey - del 1
programme.desc: Zoey må ta en avgjørelse på om hun skal bli på PCA eller flytte til London med foreldrene. Hun ber vennene sine om råd, men unngår Chase så lenge hun kan.

programme.title: Zoey 101: PCA konfidensielt
programme.desc: Fremtidige elever får se hvordan livet er på PCA.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Bytte steder
programme.desc: Zoey kommer tilbake til PCA for å snakke med Chase, men oppdager at han har blitt overført til England for å være sammen med henne.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Juksesamboeren
programme.desc: Michael og Logan prøver å lure Frøken Burvitch, for å slippe å få en ny gutt på rommet. Zoey klarer ved et uhell å få Coco sparket og prøver å hjelpe henne.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Alene på PCA
programme.desc: Alle har det kjempegøy på skolen når påskeferien hjem blir avlyst. Men så anklager rektoren guttene for vandalisme.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Kjærlighetsryktet
programme.desc: Michael og Logans nye gutt på rommet er veldig kjekk. Han blir fort en favoritt hos jentene og det liker ikke Logan noe særlig.

programme.title: Zoey 101: SInnamestring
programme.desc: Logan sender Dustin melding som gjør at han får plass i sinnemestringsklassen. Han prøver å unngå å møte opp, men Zoey har andre planer.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Quinn bommer på merket
programme.desc: Quinn og Mark blir enige om å ta en pause, men Quinn blir lei seg når hun ser ham med en annen. Quinn finner litt trøst hos Logan og de kysser. Mellomtiden følger en hest etter Michael.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Innsamlingen
programme.desc: Zoey prøver å hjelpe Lola med å finne pengene hun har lovt bort til en veldedighet organisator. Quinn og Logan begynner å nærme seg hverandre, men holder det skjult.

programme.title: Zoey 101: VInce er tilbake
programme.desc: Gjengen blir overrasket over å finne ut at en gammel bølle, Vince Blake, er tilbake på PCA. Jentene bestemmer seg for å ignorere ham, men det blir vanskeligere enn de trodde.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Kaffeforbudet
programme.desc: Rektor Rivers forbyr kaffevogner på skolen etter en ulykke. Da blir det en jente- og guttekamp om å komme opp med løsninger som gjør at det blir lov igjen.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Berg og dalbanen
programme.desc: Gjengen drar på klassetur for å kjøre berg og dalbane. Men Michael er redd og må møte frykten sin for å tørre å prøve.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Hvor er Zoey - del 1
programme.desc: Zoey planlegger en tur til Maui og James vil bli med også. Hennes reaksjon er ikke helt den han forventet. Michael får låne en gammel bil av faren for å kjøre Lisa til ballet.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Hvor er Zoey - del 2
programme.desc: Zoey planlegger en tur til Maui og James vil bli med også. Hennes reaksjon er ikke helt den han forventet. Michael får låne en gammel bil av faren for å kjøre Lisa til ballet.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Velkommen til P.C.A.
programme.desc: Zoey Brooks er en av de mange jentene som kommer til PCA for første gang. Når hun kommer dit, møter hun venner og hun får en fiende i Logan. En som tror at jenter ikke kan slå gutter i basketball.

programme.title: Zoey 101: New Roomies
programme.desc: Zoey begynner å like livet på PCA, men så viser Dana and Nicole at de ikke liker hverandre. Zoey hater den konstante kranglingen og flytter inn på Quinns rom.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Forvare Dustin
programme.desc: Dustin treffer på en bølle han har hjulpet i timen.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Skuespillet
programme.desc: Chase skriver et skuespill om en romjente med Zoey i tankene, men han synes ikke det er noe gøy når Logan får rollen som hennes jordiske kjæreste og ikke han. Quinn prøver å hjelpe ham på en litt ukonvensjonell måte.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Webkameraet
programme.desc: Zoey oppdager en god side ved Logan når han gir jentene en stor teddybjørn. Men når hemmelighetene de snakker om blir spredd rundt på skolen, blir de mistenksomme.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Jet X
programme.desc: Barna på PCA får oppdrag å lage en TV-reklame for en ny scooter.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Vårforelskelsen
programme.desc: Jentene blir med på å planlegge Vårfesten og prøver å få en kjendis til å opptre.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Lureuka
programme.desc: Guttene lurer jentene, som får jentene til å legge en djerv plan.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Quinns date
programme.desc: Quinn blir forelsket i Mark, men så finner Zoey ut at han ikke er interresert. Hun organiserer allikevel en falsk date for de to.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Ryggsekken
programme.desc: Zoeys ryggsekk blir stjålet av en ansatt i bokhandelen som later som den er hennes design.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 706
programme.desc: Kranfører Carl har blitt bedt om å flytte en havnekran som veier nesten 200 tonn og er 33 meter høy. Men arbeidet må brått avbrytes fordi det er fare for at kranen kan velte når en del mangler.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 707
programme.desc: Mattias må hente kviger i Enköping og deretter hente en okse på Ljusterö, noe som ikke viser seg å være lett.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 708
programme.desc: I Stockholm har Max en tøff dag og sliter med å få med seg alle søppeldunkene som skal tømmes. Han gleder seg til den siste tømmingen for dagen.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 201
programme.desc: Simon fra Piteå har tatt over som administrerende direktør i transportfirmaet etter sin far Erik. Jörgen fra Höganäs må kjøre et 58 meter langt blad til en vindturbin og støter på utfordringer i svingene.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 202
programme.desc: Erik Lundman i Lundmans transportfirma sliter med en kloakktank, postbud Stephanie gjør en feil og taper tid under en hastetur, og spesialtransportør Jari får utrolig nok tre punkteringer.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 203
programme.desc: Jesper er bekymret for å komme for sent til avlastningen i Danmark. Tove får en dårlig start på dagen og krasjer med tømmerbilen sin. Og Jari havner i feil havn under lossing.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 204
programme.desc: Louise har en uvanlig tung forsendelse med to ismaskiner som skal fraktes til en ishockeybane utenfor Stockholm. Robin, som kjører biler verdt millioner, har en kjøretur med en veldig fin Cobra fra 1965.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 205
programme.desc: Familiebedriften Tösse wedins har en ny kunde som trenger den erfarne tømmerbilsjåføren og administrerende direktøren i selskapet, "Höna", til å kjøre en lastebil.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 301
programme.desc: Anton og broren transporterer en gravemaskin på den lokale "Dødens vei". Sam, en miljøarbeider, er opprørt over det moderne menneskets livsstil. Og Tove drar til en skog for å samle tømmer.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 302
programme.desc: I Hässleholm skal Jörgen kjøre en bro med en uvanlig form, der du virkelig må tenke på å løfte hvis du ikke vil at sikkerhetsanordningene skal svikte.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 303
programme.desc: Stephanie guider oss gjennom vanskelighetene med å være leveringssjåfør i Stockholm. Anders kjører et stort elektrisk hus fra Öjebyn til Boliden, og det må ikke få riper.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 304
programme.desc: Anders er på vei til Boliden med en 20 tonn tung og 20 meter lang container, men til tross for forberedelser havner han på feil vei. Elin blir skikkelig stresset når hun havner midt i rushtrafikken i Stockholm.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 305
programme.desc: I Kristinehamn i Sverige er Jörgen i ferd med å laste en 135 tonn tung barktønne da et høyt smell stopper lasteprosessen. Spylebilsjåføren Magnus og kollegaen Bruno sjekker et overvannsrør.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 401
programme.desc: Å finne frem i skogen er lettere sagt enn gjort. For den nyankomne tømmerbilsjåføren Linda betyr det at hun kommer på etterskudd i et allerede stramt tidsskjema.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 402
programme.desc: I Gøteborg flytter spesialtransportøren Jonathan campinghytter, og været er ikke på hans side. I Stockholm er rotter et problem, og Max, en søppelmann, vil helst slippe å møte dem.

programme.title: Survivor: It's Getting The Best of Me
programme.desc: One Villain pushes so hard to provide for the tribe that he passes out cold. The tribe worries that their strongest asset may be taken out of the game.
programme.sub-title: It's Getting The Best of Me

programme.title: Survivor: That Girl Is Like a Virus
programme.desc: When one castaway finds himself in hot water with an ally, he must scramble to prove his loyalty. One tough Villain has the whole tribe on edge as everyone sets their sites on one very dangerous alliance.
programme.sub-title: That Girl Is Like a Virus

programme.title: Survivor: Tonight We Make Our Move
programme.desc: The Dragon Slayer reaches his breaking point and considers leaving the game. A clue to the Hidden Immunity Idol threatens to tear one tribe apart when a fight erupts about what should be done with the valuable information.

programme.title: Survivor: Knights of the Roundtable
programme.desc: In a grueling physical challenge, one castaway takes a hard fall that results in an injury so severe that it threatens to take him out of the game for good.

programme.title: Survivor: Banana Etiquette
programme.desc: The Heroes tribe continues to struggle in an effort to get their priorities straight. A division threatens to tear the tribe apart and send one of their strongest players home.

programme.title: Survivor: I'm Not A Good Villain
programme.desc: With plenty to prove to his tribe, one castaway knows that he’s been given a last chance. Will he finally come through for the team?

programme.title: Survivor: Expectations
programme.desc: Both tribes find themselves eagerly anticipating the merge and arrive at the Reward Challenge ready for a big announcement. Struggling to keep their tribe in tact, the Heroes vow to work together to ensure that they outlast the Villains.

programme.title: Survivor: Survivor History
programme.desc: Reeling from the loss of an ally, one castaway scrambles to secure votes, fearing that she might be the next target. The Heroes develop a risky strategy in an effort to align themselves with one of the game’s most notorious players.

programme.title: Survivor: Going Down In Flames
programme.desc: A Hero finds himself taking a gamble and placing trust in one of the game’s most notorious villains, despite objections from his wary alliance.

programme.title: Survivor: Jumping Ship
programme.desc: In the wake of a game-changing Tribal Council, everyone struggles to find their place in the newly merged tribe and some panicked players consider making new allies in an effort to regain control of the game.

programme.title: Survivor: Sinking Ship
programme.desc: Reeling from the departure of their ally, two castaways are forced to rethink their plans now that their alliance has been shattered.

programme.title: Survivor: Loose Lips Sink Ships
programme.desc: The final six get the chance to earn time with their loved ones in a fiercely fought reward challenge. One castaway makes a surprising choice that sends ripples through the tribe and threatens to cost someone the million dollar prize.

programme.title: Survivor: Anything Could Happen
programme.desc: One castaway lets paranoia get the best of him as he targets a loyal ally. As the final tribal council draws near, everyone struggles to stay on top of their game as alliances crumble and everyone starts to play the game for themselves.

programme.title: Survivor: Reunion
programme.desc: A one-hour live reunion.

programme.title: Survivor: Blood Is Thicker Than Anything
programme.desc: In a Survivor first, former castaways are stranded deep in the jungle with only their loved ones.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Break the unbreakable wall!
programme.desc: With their firepower boosted by the addition of Jude Sharp, the team are ready to tackle Farm Jr High and their unbreakable defence. But unless they get their passes coordinated then all their hard work will come to nothing!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The reincarnated genius!
programme.desc: Erik the Eagle is back! Like a phoenix he has risen from the ashes and come back to visit his old friend. Just in time too, Raimon Jr are desperate for some new moves, and the Tri Pegasus is just what they need. But can they perfect it in time?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The killer Triangle Z!
programme.desc: Raimon Jr are getting ready to play their next big opponent - Kirkwood Jr High, which just happens to be Axel Blaze’s old school.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The clash with Kirkwood Jr. High!
programme.desc: The Murdock brothers and their grudge are dominating Raimon Jr. at every turn, but they need to find the strength to overcome their malice if they’re going to make it to the final. If they don’t work together, their dream is finished!
programme.sub-title: The clash with Kirkwood Jr. High!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Go beyond the God Hand!
programme.desc: Raimon Jr. are through to the finals, but they’re all getting nervous about playing the terrifying Zeus Jr. Mark is convinced he’s not good enough, and if that weren’t enough to rattle nerves

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: A challenge from a God!
programme.desc: As the final against Zeus draws nearer, so does Raimon Jr’s anticipation and dread. The team are working hard, but the level they have to reach seems beyond their grasp. Will they get it together in time for the final?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Time for training camp!
programme.desc: The big game is almost on top of them but Mark still hasn’t mastered Majin the Hand. The coach decides to try and new tactic and everyone spends the night at school at a sleepover training camp.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The final battle!
programme.desc: This is it, the final of the Nationals has arrived. Zeus Jr. storm to an early lead and nothing Raimon Jr does has any effect on them. Are they really gods? Or is something else going on?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: God vs Majin!
programme.desc: Raimon Jr. are down by three goals and are getting clobbered by the soccer gods of Zeus Jr. The situation looks completely hopeless and the clock is running down.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Aliens Are Here!
programme.desc: The victory for the Raimon 11 proves to be very short lived, as only a few minutes after their win, the sky falls in. Literally! - All of a sudden the earth is overrun by aliens!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Raimon 11 Fight Back!
programme.desc: The Raimon 11 have stepped up to try and save the world against the soccer players of Alius Academy, but it’s like pitting an ant against an elephant.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Take Down the Black 11!
programme.desc: The president has been kidnapped by aliens, and Mark and the others are determined to help him. The Inazuma Caravan travels to the park where he was kidnapped, ready to beat the aliens off.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Alius Academy Threat
programme.desc: The tenacious Raimon 11 players never give up, and they’re going to try again against Alius Academy. But try as they might they can't even hold a candle to them.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Search for the Legendary Striker!
programme.desc: The news that Axel is kicked off the team doesn’t go over well with most of the Raimon players, especially Kevin Dragonfly.
programme.sub-title: The Search for the Legendary Striker!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Prince of Snow Land!
programme.desc: Raimon are excited and surprised when they finally meet Shawn Frost, but is he really as good as everyone says? There’s only one way to find out, and that’s to play a game against him.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Who is the New Ace Striker?
programme.desc: Shawn Frost is officially part of the Raimon 11, but there are still some teamwork kinks to iron out.
programme.sub-title: Who is the New Ace Striker?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Alius Academy Attack!
programme.desc: Raimon have toughened up though their snowboard training and are ready to face Alius Academy one more time. But do they have what it takes to beat them?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Epsilon Attacks!
programme.desc: Just when everyone thought the earth had been saved, Alius Academy attack once more, but this time with Team Epsilon. These guys really mean business, and they’re beating up on a new school - Cloister Divinity in Kyoto.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Hidden Power!
programme.desc: After the crushing defeat of Cloister Divinity, Raimon step up to fill the hole, with Scotty the substitute helping out on Celia’s urging. The results are strange and disheartening, but also encouraging in one way.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Royal Academy’s Comeback - Part 1!
programme.desc: Looks like Team Raimon have a new member, in the form of Sneaky Scotty. They’ll need all the help they can get though, because Ray Dark is back on the scene, in an unfeasibly silly submarine-based soccer stadium.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Royal Academy’s Comeback Part 2!
programme.desc: Raimon are smack in the middle of a game against Royal Academy Redux, and Ray Dark has convinced its players to use any and every means to win; even if it means the destruction of their minds and bodies.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Last Wyvern Blizzard!
programme.desc: The Inazuma Caravan finally comes home to recharge their batteries and…train a whole lot more. They find out that everybody’s been training to help them, including some old enemies!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Erik Eagle in Serious Trouble!
programme.desc: No sooner do they arrive home, and they’re back on the road again - this time they’re heading to Osaka where it’s rumoured that Alius Academy have a base.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Dvalin’s Trap!
programme.desc: The team find that the Golden Glamour Girls’ secret training bunker under the amusement park is a great place to train, but where did it come from?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Epsilon - The Toughest Battle Yet!
programme.desc: The big game against Epsilon is here, and Raimon come out with all guns blazing! Will their guns be enough to turn back the alien scourge?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Grandpa’s Secret Trick!
programme.desc: Unexpected news about the existence of another David Evans notebook sends the team scurrying off to Fukuoka, where they meet one of Mark’s grandfather’s old friends, and someone who might just become Mark’s apprentice.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Other Majin the Hand!
programme.desc: The exhibition game between Raimon and Fauxshore Jr - AKA the battle of the goalies - is a knuckle biting affair. Both Mark and Darren are showing off their old moves and trying to learn new ones while a storm of shots rages around them.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Seismic Earthquake Shocker!
programme.desc: Just when Raimon were feeling confident, they get a wake up call in the form of a big slap in the face from Xavier and his Genesis team. Sure, part of being a winning team is being able to cope with loss, but a loss this big?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Captain’s Test!
programme.desc: Disaster after disaster is hitting the Raimon team hard. First Nathan decides to quit, then another member decides he can't take it anymore. Mark is in crisis and can't deal with everything that’s happening.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: Dark Signs, Part 4
programme.desc: The safety of the world hangs in the balance as Yusei tries to figure out a way to outduel and outmaneuver the unstoppable power of Kalin's dark deck.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: Supersensory Shakedown
programme.desc: Leo is forced to take part in an extrasensory examination with the leader of the Arcadia Movement. Can Leo pass this pop quiz, or will this psychic showdown with Sayer leave Leo locked up forever?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Dreaded Royal Academy!
programme.desc: The match begins, and Sam just barely manages to block a shot on goal -- Royal Academy is proving to be unlike any other team Raimon has faced.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Explosion Ultimate Thunder!
programme.desc: Raimon attempts a comeback using their super tactic, but end up surrendering a goal to Royal Academy instead. Raimon's offense is powerless in the face of Royal Academy's overwhelming special moves.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: A Revolutionary Wind!
programme.desc: The day after their blistering battle in the regional semifinals, the Raimon players are ordered to meet at Royal Academy. There, they learn the stunning truth behind their match with the academy.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 1
programme.desc: Sylvio finally has just the thing to take Yuya down – a deck full of Pendulum Cards! Could Yuya's days in the spotlight be done for?
programme.sub-title: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 2
programme.desc: Yuya is off his game and on the run as Sylvio zeroes in on zeroing out his life points! If Yuya can’t get into the swing of things, this could be his final performance!
programme.sub-title: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 2

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Making the Cut: Part 1
programme.desc: Sora is psyched to put on a showstopping duel for the fans, but his opponent Shay is set to turn Sora’s one man show into a no man show!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Making the Cut: Part 2
programme.desc: Sora and Shay's heated duel hits its boiling point when dark secrets about their hidden history come to light! Could there be something sinister behind Sora’s sweet-toothed smile?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Sora’s Secrets: Part 1
programme.desc: While Yuto is looking for answers, Sora is looking to get some revenge! But when these two tangle, Yuya finds out more than he ever expected!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Sora’s Secrets: Part 2
programme.desc: Surprises are in the cards as the battle between Sora and Yuto comes to an unexpected conclusion! But just when Yuya thinks he’s seen everything, a new face shows up on the scene that makes Yuya do a triple take!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Ravaging Fangs of the Sea Kings!
programme.desc: Determined to free Football from the clutches of Fifth Sector, the Raimon Eleven prepare to revolt. With the regional championship against Pirates Cove Merchant Marine Academy Academy coming up, morale is high, and losing is not an option.
programme.sub-title: Ravaging Fangs of the Sea Kings!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Fly Arion’s Fighting Spirit
programme.desc: The true revolution won't occur until the crowds watching are reminded of the power of real Football and decide to take a stand. The Raimon Eleven welcome back members who had quit, and the regional championship match begins.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Autumn Sky Challengers!
programme.desc: The Holy Road tournament is finally underway. Surrounded by powerful enemies sent by Fifth Sector, the matches ahead will be the toughest yet. So the team practices harder than ever, reminding themselves that no opponent is unbeatable.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Doomsday Day, Part 2
programme.desc: Jaden continues his duel against the Shadow Rider known as Nightshroud, who has extra mysteries of his own!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Field of Screams, Part 1
programme.desc: A vampiress named Camula is the second Shadow Rider to arrive at Duel Academy, but she's not there to suck blood, she's there to suck up souls!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Field of Screams, Part 2
programme.desc: Camula continues to wreak havoc at Duel Academy, this time setting her sights on Zane.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Field of Screams, Part 3
programme.desc: Jaden steps up to confront Camula with the souls of Dr. Crowler and Zane at stake.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: The Fear Factor
programme.desc: Jaden and the gang get sucked into a strange vortex where a duelist who bears a striking resemblance to Kaiba forces Jaden to face his worst fears or be overcome by them!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Sibling Rivalry
programme.desc: Chazz's brothers have come back to Duel Academy for revenge, forcing Chazz to face them in a duel where if he loses, the deed to Duel Academy will be passed to them!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Gather, At The Flag Of Revolution
programme.desc: After seeing the newcomer's strange behavior in a practice match with the residents of ''Windsor Manor' flats, Bagriel Garcia (Gabi) begins to suspect the boy may be a Seed agent sent by Fifth Sector.
programme.sub-title: Gather, At The Flag Of Revolution

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Fearsome Cyclone Arena
programme.desc: The first round of the Holy Road tournament gets underway at Aerodrome Arena. The Raimon Eleven are put on the defensive by Lunar Sea (Military) Academy's formations and attacks, which take full advantage of special contraptions unique to the venue.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Revive Our Football!
programme.desc: Raimon uses Aitor and Gabi's stellar tandem skills to combat Lunar Sea's tactical play. When Arion uses his Fighting Spirit to even the score, momentum shifts to Raimon.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Showdown in the Sewers
programme.desc: Ghost Gal puts her data on the line when she Speed Duels against Varis in the sewers of LINK VRAINS!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: The Tower of Hanoi
programme.desc: The Hanoi’s greatest weapon is about to be unleashed unless Yusaku can link into the VRAINS and stop it!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Once Upon A Time
programme.desc: As Blue Angel's biggest fan, Spectre knows all her dueling tricks and techniques - which makes him the fiercest foe she's ever faced!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Roots of Evil
programme.desc: Spectre knows Blue Angel's entire life story, and he’s going to give it a sad ending!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: The Hollow
programme.desc: Playmaker must cut down Spectre’s defenses if he is to topple the Tower of Hanoi!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: A Bridge Too Far
programme.desc: Spectre stoops to a new low when he reveals a game changer that leaves Playmaker without a play to make!

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 11
programme.desc: Sister Benita Wainwright is leading the team, a day that she describes as “Chaos. There are people everywhere. It’s hard going. But staff pull together and make sure patients are looked after.”

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 12
programme.desc: At Barnsley Casualty the team clock on to a backlog of patients waiting to be transferred to wards. With no beds across the entire hospital, Sister Jane Hawksworth is battling to prevent patients being on trolleys for the NHS maximum of 12 hours.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 13
programme.desc: After an extraordinarily busy few days, the team at Barnsley Casualty are struggling to clear the backlog of patients, and new arrivals are waiting up to 5 hours to see a doctor.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 14
programme.desc: Sister Jane Hawksworth is on duty, ‘I think the sister team is strong, we are all strong women.' Sister Benita Wainwright heads to Resus where paramedics rush in a 14-year-old girl having a prolonged epileptic seizure.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 15
programme.desc: It’s been a busy night at Barnsley Hospital’s Casualty Department, so the corridors are already packed full of patients when Sister Benita Wainwright arrives to head the shift.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 16
programme.desc: In charge today at Barnsley Hospital’s Casualty Department is Consultant Doctor Julian Humphrey, ‘Emergency departments may look very chaotic but there’s a reasonable amount of structure. It’s organized chaos!’

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 17
programme.desc: Barnsley Casualty is facing one of its toughest shifts to date. With no children’s beds available across the whole of Yorkshire and a department filling up with poorly children the hospital is under pressure.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 18
programme.desc: Registrar Doctor Gemma Hartshorne prepares to treat a man who has suddenly lost all feeling in his foot. Loss of blood flow is turning Roger's foot white - urgent treatment is needed to prevent amputation.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 19
programme.desc: Trainee Advanced Nurse Practitioner Chantelle Proctor assesses a 49-year-old man rushed in by ambulance. Philip, who has a heart condition, collapsed at home and has been vomiting for the last ten days.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 20
programme.desc: While people enjoy a most wonderful time of the year, Barnsley Hospital Casualty is open for business as usual, and the team are getting into the Christmas spirit. Consultant Doctor Julian Humphrey is leading the festive shift.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 1
programme.desc: While Sister Jane runs outside to help a critical patient in the car park, Matron Val and Consultant Doctor Dave Walker need to negotiate with the Police who are stopping new arrivals entering the building.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 2
programme.desc: Junior Doctor Tom Fish’s first patient is 18-year-old Lewis who has broken bones and deep wounds from a moped accident - but causing him the most pain is his fear of needles.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 3
programme.desc: Sister Benita is running the shift, when suddenly, a fire alarm goes off and she must prepare the entire department - staff and emergency patients - for a full evacuation.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 4
programme.desc: Sister Harriet spots Terry waiting in the queue and decides he needs urgent care. He’s fallen off a roof and is unable to move his arm from a position above his head.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 1
programme.desc: Hoarding is on the rise and it's believed that 1 in 20 people could have a problem. With over 1.2 million problem hoarders in the UK today, one could be your neighbour?

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 2
programme.desc: Susan's hoard has made her virtually homeless. Brian has dedicated his life to hoarding and his daughter is sick of it. Jake is lucky to be alive as his home almost burned to the ground in an inferno fuelled by the clutter he'd collected.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 3
programme.desc: Arthur's flat is packed with junk. Experts Caz and Tee are up for their toughest assignment ever. Khim is getting married but first she must clear her hoard. Mandi's passion for vintage clothes is out of control.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 4
programme.desc: Esther's hoard is so bad her landlord told her to clear up or clear out. Nigel receives a visit from fellow hoarder Janice.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 5
programme.desc: Paul's hoard fills his whole house, room after room after room is buried under 6 feet of clutter.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 6
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of American born dog loving Dani from Shepton Mallet who moved to the UK with high hopes of living the English Country dream, but bad health got the better of her.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 7
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Eco warrior Karen from Somerset, who after many years of living off grid in a caravan, has struggled to adapt to living in, and looking after, a house.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 8
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Pippa and Matt from Oxford who have 6 kids all living in a 3-bedroom house. With both parents working full time, the house has taken a back seat for many years.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 1
programme.desc: In the picturesque city of Bath, Paul’s cottage is bursting at the seams with a lifetime’s collection of junk. Known locally as ‘boot cottage’ - because everything Paul owns and wears comes from car boot sales - every room is a no-go zone.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 2
programme.desc: In Harlow, 63-year-old Bubbles’ high-rise flat is packed with piles of junk she can’t bear to throw away. But it doesn’t end there she also has a staggering 4 lock ups stuffed to the gills with rubbish.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 3
programme.desc: In Mansfield Sue’s hoard is driving her family and grandchildren away and her husband Neil to distraction. Every room is crammed with clutter including a bedroom that looks more like a dolls graveyard than somewhere to sleep.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 4
programme.desc: In Liverpool, the Bells are a family at war over hoarding. Mum Betty and son Richard are happy to live in their mess, but son in law Keith is determined that things must change. Can they change the habit of a lifetime and part with their possessions?

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 5
programme.desc: In the London suburb of Enfield, former workaholic Sandra has become a hoard-aholic since retiring. Her compulsion to spend is out of control, and everything is added to the growing mountains of books, clothes and candles…

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 1
programme.desc: In this brand-new series of Dirty Home Rescue, Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Toni from Telford whose house is so dirty her partner of 10 years, Rich, won’t move in with her.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 2
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Bill and Antionette from Newport, who share their home with their 3 cats. They admit they’ve not deep cleaned their home since they moved in.

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 705
programme.desc: Psykolog Helena Bering forsvinner sporløst midt på dagen den 18. august 2004. Hun har nettopp avsluttet et møte med en klient på klinikken i Stockholm, når alle spor etter henne forsvinner.

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 706
programme.desc: I mai 2017 ble småbarnsfaren Filip Viking funnet skutt i Katrineholm. Vitner skynder seg bort til ham og i forbindelse med forsøkene på å redde Filips liv, klarer de å se en lang svartkledd mann løpe fra åstedet.

programme.title: Norske Krimsaker: Episode 403
programme.desc: Marit Ødegaard jobber på en veikro ikke langt fra svenskegrensen. En oktoberdag i 2000 dukker hun ikke opp på jobb. Kort tid etter blir Marit funnet drept i hjemmet sitt

programme.title: Norske Krimsaker: Episode 404
programme.desc: I desember 2015 gjør gallerist Reidar Osen et ærend med varebilen sin da han blir kapret av ukjente gjerningsmenn, som truer ham på livet og krever to millioner kroner. Hvem står bak kidnappingen?

programme.title: Norske Krimsaker: Episode 405
programme.desc: To reindriftsutøvere fra Vest Finnmark havner i politiets søkelys etter å ha innrapportert flere hundre rovdyrskadde reinsdyr. Kan det virkelig være slik at de to har mishandlet dyrene sine for å motta erstatning?

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 504
programme.desc: Ungdommene Abbas og Sina forelsker seg i hverandre, men Sinas familie forbyr forholdet og paret bestemmer seg for å flykte. Men vil familien la det skje uten å ta opp jakten på dem?

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 505
programme.desc: Før jul i 2000 blir Nasjonalmuseet utsatt for Sveriges største kunstkupp noensinne. Kunstverk til en verdi av 370 millioner svenske kroner forsvinner. Nå må politiet gjøre alt de kan for å løse saken.

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 506
programme.desc: En ung kvinne blir funnet drept utenfor en gymsal i Nacka. Når politiet begynner å grave i fortiden hennes, oppdager de at noen betraktet henne på avstand. En person fylt av sjalusi.

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 507
programme.desc: 25 år gamle Anna blir funnet brutalt myrdet i sin nye leilighet i Karlstad. Når politiet etterforsker drapet, tyder alt på at gjerningsmannen kan være en person hun har møtt tidligere.

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 601
programme.desc: Den 14. november 2019 forsvinner sytten år gamle Wilma, og hele Uddevalla blir involvert i forsvinningen. Etter noen dager blir det funnet blod i hennes og kjærestens leilighet, men Wilma er fortsatt savnet.

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 602
programme.desc: En regnfull morgen den 19. oktober 2004 dreper en ukjent mann en åtte år gammel gutt og en 56 år gammel kvinne i Linköping. Gjerningsmannen forsvinner sporløst og politiet må nå finne ut hvem han er.

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 603
programme.desc: Politiet har ikke gitt opp å oppklare dobbeltdrapet i Linköping. Etter en endring i svensk lov i 2019, har politiet nå muligheten til å bruke kommersielle slektsdatabaser for å finne gjerningsmannen.

programme.title: Norske Krimsaker: Episode 304
programme.desc: I august 2004 stormer to bevæpnede personer inn i Munch-museet på Tøyen. I kaoset som oppstår tar de med seg de to verdenskjente maleriene Skrik og Madonna. Hvem står bak tyveriet, og er bildene tapt for alltid?

programme.title: Norske Krimsaker: Episode 401
programme.desc: I mai 1995 blir 17 år gamle Birgitte Tengs funnet drept bare noen få hundre meter unna sitt hjem i Kopervik på Karmøy. Saken fører til omfattende etterforskning, og Birgittes fetter havner raskt i søkelyset.

programme.title: Norske Krimsaker: Episode 402
programme.desc: En sommerdag i 1999 sykler tolv år gamle Kristin Juel Johannessen hjemmefra på vei til badestranda. Samme kveld blir hun meldt savnet. Hvor har den unge jenta tatt veien?

programme.title: Svenske krimsaker: Episode 405
programme.desc: Politiet har pågrepet mannen kjent som "35-åringen" for drapet på Anna Lindh. Samtidig har noen venner av en "Micke" reagert på at vennen deres oppfører seg merkelig og varsler politiet.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Charlotte, Elvis and Jack
programme.desc: Actress Eileen Davidson's Wheaten terrier puppy Charlotte, plays too rough with her son. Two other dogs react to household triggers, the garbage disposal and shiny floors.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Cesar and the Horse Whisperer (Chloe & Hobo, Ali)
programme.desc: Cesar enlists the help of Horse Whisperer Pat Parelli at a riding center that works with special needs people. A dog with separation anxiety exhibits extreme dog aggression.
programme.sub-title: Cesar and the Horse Whisperer (Chloe & Hobo, Ali)

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Inside Puppy Mills
programme.desc: This powerful episode delves into the horror of puppy mills and the rescue and rehab of traumatized pups by the Last Chance for Animals non-profit organization.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Nuna & Kane
programme.desc: NuNu the Chihuahua, fiercely attacks anyone who comes near his owner Tina. NuNu’s total opposite, Kane the Great Dane, is vehemently afraid of shiny surfaces

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Opie & Flirt
programme.desc: Black lab mix Opie is a charmer around people, but frighteningly aggressive around other dogs. Energetic to the point of being neurotic, Chinese Crested Flirt cannot sit still for one moment.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Rana & Ruby
programme.desc: Scared of everything, Ruby the Vischla deals with her neuroses by biting. At the same time, Rana barks every time bread pops in the toaster, or when the microwave goes off, or when the phone rings.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Josh & Boomer
programme.desc: Josh, a Maltese, will not let anyone with a brush or pair of scissors near him without putting up a fight. Boomer, a Chesapeake Bay Retriever, barks incessantly and refuses to come out of the pool.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Harry & Brooks
programme.desc: Harry wants to charge after anything with wheels, including passing cyclists, rollerbladers or skateboarders. Brooks, an Entlebucher, is constantly chasing after light, he is never calm.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Coach & Sueki
programme.desc: Coach, an out of control Boxer, bit a neighbor, seemingly sealing his fate. Coach gets a stay of execution when Cesar Millan comes to the rescue. Sueki refuses to walk on the leash.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Slick & Pepper
programme.desc: Slick, a rare white Puli, is full of phobias. When clients come to Christopher’s photography studio, they are greeted by Pepper’s annoying barking and heel nipping.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Ava & Gus
programme.desc: Ava, a Pug/Pekingese swiftly twirls for all occasions, possibly a neurological condition Cesar cannot treat. Gus the Bouvier greets people by throwing his 100 pound body at them.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Maya & Churchill
programme.desc: Churchill the Rottweiler is a well mannered dog, except when around other animals. Meanwhile, Maya, an affable Pit Bull, insists on being intimately involved in all operations of the household.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Bubba & Garrett
programme.desc: Heidi Wasserman inherited Bubba, a spoiled Maltese that demands to be taken everywhere and nips at anyone who tries to leave. Garrett, a German Shepherd, chases his tail, obsessively.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Emily
programme.desc: Emily, a Pit Bull, has become every owner’s worst nightmare – extremely aggressive towards other dogs. She’s so out of control, only Cesar Millan’s 6-week boot camp can turn her behavior around.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Hank & Paris
programme.desc: Marsha Alexander’s rescued Mastiff has ruined the furniture and intimidates anyone walking by his gate. Paris, a long hair Chihuahua, looks fashionable, but barks and snaps at strangers.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Sasha & Shep
programme.desc: Lhasa Apso Sasha, bares her teeth at anyone who takes anything from her. White German Shepherd, “Shep,” goes after strangers, making it impossible for his wheelchair bound owner to control.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Jake & King
programme.desc: Jake tends to mind his owner Bob but goes crazy to protect Bob’s wife Linda. At the same time, all of 10 year old Chantel’s might is hardly enough for 150 pound King to even take notice.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Scrawny & Lola
programme.desc: Scrawny, one of nine Yorkies, is Allen’s favorite, but attacks anyone that comes near. Lola, a Dalmatian, barks at everything. Find out how Cesar reestablishes control in both homes.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: J & Alice
programme.desc: J is unpredictable and aggressive and his owner is now dealing with a lawsuit. Alice is depressed and aggressive towards the other two dogs in the house – a potentially lethal combination.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Caper & Julius
programme.desc: Caper has a lot of energy, particularly when it comes to chasing down balls non-stop. Julius is a four-year-old Pit Bull mix that is frightened of everything.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Bella & Jordan
programme.desc: “Bella Angel” is a devil in disguise. She bites anyone who comes near the house or the family. Jordan, an English Bulldog, jumps up and down, licks people incessantly and is obsessed by skateboards.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Sunshine & Teddy
programme.desc: Sunshine is a champion Doberman in the show ring but far too aggressive in the street. Teddy, a yellow lab, has bitten its owner twice, and has attacked more than one stranger.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Goldie & Pepsi
programme.desc: Pepsi, a German Shepherd, becomes intensely aggressive around cats. Goldie, the beautiful Brittany Spaniel of “General Hospital” star Jacklyn Zeman that has become aggressive towards female dogs.

programme.title: South Park: Sparkesyklene

programme.title: South Park: Heksesønner

programme.title: South Park: De levende hjemløses natt

programme.title: South Park: Døde kjendiser
programme.desc: Michael Jacksons spøkelse nekter å akseptere å måtte vandre heden og etterlater resten av de nylig avdøde berømtheter frustrert i Skjærsilden.

programme.title: South Park: Døden

programme.desc: Det er Halloween i South Park, og Kenny blir drept av en styrtende romstasjon og forvandlet til en zombie, ved hjelp av balsameringsvæske og Worcestersaus.

programme.title: South Park: Gothbarn 3: posørenes daggry

programme.desc: Cartman skryter av sin nye Trapper Keeper, men en fremmed forteller ham at den snart vil ta over verden om de ikke ødelegger den nå.

programme.title: South Park: Tegridy Farms Halloween Special

programme.title: South Park: Pandemien
programme.desc: South Park tar en 'Cloverfield' med store, mystiske skapninger som herjer rundt i verden og blir fanget opp av Randys kamera.

programme.title: South Park: Et mareritt på Face Time
programme.desc: Randys store planer for Halloween gjør at Stan ikke får gå 'Knask eller knep' med vennene sine.

programme.title: South Park: Succubusen
programme.desc: Cartman går til optiker, som gjør narr av Cartmans vektproblemer og kaller ham 'Piggy'.

programme.title: South Park: Korns kule piratspøkelsesmysterium
programme.desc: Guttene plages av femteklassinger, og South Park blir oversvømt av piratspøkelser i denne halloween-episoden.

programme.desc: Evig uskyldige Butters er lei behandlingen han får av foreldrene, og blir litt for oppslukt av den nye vampyrfeberen.

programme.desc: Kennys foreldre blir arrestert og han plasseres i fosterhjem - så nå er Cartman det fattigste barnet på skolen! I mellomtiden kommer en mystisk figur fra fortiden tilbake.

programme.title: South Park: Pandemien 2: Alarmerende
programme.desc: Enorme marsvin angriper byer i hele verden. Guttene har nøkkelen til å redde menneskeheten, men sitter fast i Andesfjellene.
